race.description: Kilcoy Free Entry Harness 26 Oct Hcp (55)
race.comment: Open race to close out the card. GRANDEUR ROSE (10) has a solid record at this circuit with three wins and four placings from 14 spins and gets in well at the weights with the 1.5kg claim. Maps well for this from gate five and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. ARTOPIA (9) will strip fitter third-up from the spell and is drawn favourably for hoop Tilley in gate two. Sure to give backers a sight. MISS ZERMATT (6) resumes here but has won two from three when first-up and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. BEE EXACT (3) is a bit hit or miss but has saluted over this track and trip and can feature if he brings his A-game.
